eb/API/MediaStreamTrack/getConstraints\"><code>getConstraints()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaStreamTrack/getSettings\"><code>getSettings()</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaStreamTrack/stop\"><code>stop()</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>イベント</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaStreamTrack/ended_event\"><code>ended</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaStreamTrack/mute_event\"><code>mute</code></a></li><li><svg class=\"icon icon-deprecated\" tabindex=\"0\">\n    <use xlink:href=\"/assets/badges.svg#icon-deprecated\"></use>\n</svg><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaStreamTrack/overconstrained_event\"><code>overconstrained</code></a></li><li><em><code>unmute</code></em></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>継承</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></li></ol></details></li><li class=\"toggle\"><details open=\"\"><summary>Media Capture and Streams に関連するページ</summary><ol><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/BlobEvent\"><code>BlobEvent</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/CanvasCaptureMediaStreamTrack\"><code>CanvasCaptureMediaStreamTrack</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/HTMLCanvasElement/captureStream\"><code>HTMLCanvasElement.captureStream()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaDevices\"><code>MediaDevices</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaDevices/getUserMedia\"><code>MediaDevices.getUserMedia()</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaStream\"><code>MediaStream</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaStreamTrackEvent\"><code>MediaStreamTrackEvent</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"この項目についての文書はまだ書かれていません。書いてみませんか？\"><code>MediaTrackCapabilities</code></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaTrackConstraints\"><code>MediaTrackConstraints</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/API/MediaTrackSettings\"><code>MediaTrackSettings</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/MediaTrackSupportedConstraints\"><code>MediaTrackSupportedConstraints</code></a></li><li><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Navigator/mediaDevices\"><code>Navigator.mediaDevices</code></a></li><li><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"この項目についての文書はまだ書かれていません。書いてみませんか？\"><code>VideoStreamTrack</code></a></li></ol></details></li></ol>","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>\n\n<p><code><strong>MediaStreamTrack.onunmute</strong></code>イベントハンドラは<code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Reference/Events/unmute\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">unmute</a></code>イベントを受け取った時に呼び出されるプロパティです。このイベントは、トラックが再びデータを送信できるようになった時に発生します。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"文法","title":"文法","isH3":false,"content":"<pre class=\"eval notranslate\"><em>track</em>.onunmute = <em>function</em>;\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"値","title":"値","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li><code>function</code>はユーザーが定義した関数の名前で末尾の<code>()</code>やパラメータを省略したもの、または、<code>function(event) {...}</code>の形式で表現された匿名関です。イベントハンドラは常に 、<a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a>型のイベントを含む1つのパラメータを持ちます。</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"例","title":"例","isH3":false,"content":"<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>dc<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function-variable function\">onunmute</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token keyword\">function</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">ev</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span> <span class=\"token function\">alert</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">\"unmute event detected!\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n</code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"specifications","title":"仕様","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\" style=\"height: 49px; width: 1000px;\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">仕様</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">状況</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">コメント</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><a href=\"https://w3c.github.io/mediacapture-main/#widl-MediaStreamTrack-onunmute\" hreflang=\"en\" lang=\"en\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Media Capture and Streams<br><small lang=\"ja\">MediaStreamTrack.onunmute の定義</small></a></td>\n   <td><span class=\"spec-cr\">勧告候補</span></td>\n   <td>初版</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"ブラウザ互換性","id":"ブラウザ互換性","isH3":false,"query":"api.MediaStreamTrack.onunmute","dataURL":"/ja/docs/conflicting/Web/API/MediaStreamTrack/unmute_event/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"関連項目","title":"関連項目","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><code><a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/Reference/Events/unmute\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">unmute</a></code>イベント、およびその型である<a href=\"/ja/docs/Web/API/Event\"><code>Event</code></a>。</li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"文法","id":"文法"},{"text":"例","id":"例"},{"text":"仕様","id":"specifications"},{"text":"ブラウザ互換性","id":"ブラウザ互換性"},{"text":"関連項目","id":"関連項目"}],"summary":"MediaStreamTrack.onunmuteイベントハンドラはunmuteイベントを受け取った時に呼び出されるプロパティです。このイベントは、トラックが再びデータを送信できるようになった時に発生します。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","source":{"folder":"ja/conflicting/web/api/mediastreamtrack/unmute_event","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/ja/conflicting/web/api/mediastreamtrack/unmute_event/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"pageTitle":"MediaStreamTrack.onunmute | MDN","noIndexing":true}}